around the table.

52
00:03:17.745 --> 00:03:21.734
taking a team...

53
00:03:21.817 --> 00:03:23.852
and making it into a family.

54
00:03:26.137 --> 00:03:27.674
And now we've got this plaque...

55
00:03:29.128 --> 00:03:31.414
...to tell anyone who
walks through these doors

56
00:03:31.497 --> 00:03:32.950
what we already know:

57
00:03:35.941 --> 00:03:38.310
This is Bobby's house.

58
00:03:54.179 --> 00:03:56.008
Bobby would have hated
his name on the wall.

59
00:03:56.091 --> 00:03:57.960
Maybe not as much as I do.

60
00:03:58.043 --> 00:03:58.999
Hey.

61
00:03:59.082 --> 00:04:01.118
he deserves his
name on the wall.

62
00:04:01.200 --> 00:04:02.696
and you have done a great job

63
