together since he's been gone.

64
00:04:05.230 --> 00:04:07.598
He would be really proud of you.

65
00:04:08.595 --> 00:04:10.756
Maybe not as proud as I am.

66
00:04:13.664 --> 00:04:15.118
Well. they all
don't hate me yet.

67
00:04:15.201 --> 00:04:17.777
Chim. the vibes here are good.

68
00:04:17.860 --> 00:04:20.435
Really good.

69
00:04:20.518 --> 00:04:22.389
That partnership

70
00:04:22.471 --> 00:04:23.552
