Yeah.

72
00:04:25.670 --> 00:04:27.914
I don't know why I was worried.

73
00:04:27.997 --> 00:04:30.905
I'm not saying it's a
bad thing. I just think

74
00:04:30.988 --> 00:04:32.941
-it's kind of weird. you know?
-No.

75
00:04:33.024 --> 00:04:34.229
-Jinx!
-Jinx!

76
00:04:35.724 --> 00:04:37.885
Usually. when you start

77
00:04:37.967 --> 00:04:39.131
