78
00:04:39.213 --> 00:04:40.751
it takes a while to
get used to each other.

79
00:04:40.834 --> 00:04:42.081
To find a rhythm.

80
00:04:42.164 --> 00:04:44.240
but no. not with the
dream team over there.

81
00:04:44.323 --> 00:04:46.858
They act like they've been
working together for years.

82
00:04:46.941 --> 00:04:48.728
They have been working
together for years.

83
00:04:48.810 --> 00:04:52.217
You've all been working
together for years.

84
00:04:53.754 --> 00:04:54.668
You're both seniors now. right?

85
00:04:54.751 --> 00:04:55.874
Well. I actually should have

86
