get a bigger place.

90
00:05:03.351 --> 00:05:04.805
A man needs his own bathroom.

91
00:05:04.888 --> 00:05:06.675
You're not living with your mom?

92
00:05:06.758 --> 00:05:08.835
Well. I didn't want
to switch schools. so

93
00:05:08.918 --> 00:05:11.286
Mom's been letting me crash
at May's since the fire.

94
00:05:11.368 --> 00:05:14.693
Well. you give her my best.

95
00:05:14.776 --> 00:05:16.022
I'm sorry I didn't
get to see her today.

96
00:05:16.105 --> 00:05:17.683
Us. too.

97
00:05:20.716 --> 00:05:22.711
I just tried calling her
again and it keeps going

98
00:05:22.793 --> 00:05:23.916
