remembering Bobby.

108
00:05:49.589 --> 00:05:52.000
You are really extraordinary.

109
00:05:52.083 --> 00:05:53.910
Oh.

110
00:05:53.993 --> 00:05:57.483
You know. for months I've been
swiping right. and nothing.

111
00:05:57.566 --> 00:05:59.104
Then. I turn left
at a farmers market

112
