believe those odds.

114
00:06:04.629 --> 00:06:07.121
I can't believe this
is just our first date.

115
00:06:07.204 --> 00:06:09.821
Well. here's to a second.

116
00:06:09.904 --> 00:06:11.775
Mm. Oh!

117
00:06:11.857 --> 00:06:13.229
-Oh.
-Oh. my Lord.

118
00:06:13.312 --> 00:06:15.181
-Oh.
-Oh.

119
00:06:15.264 --> 00:06:16.885
-Oh. I'm so sorry.
-It's okay. It's okay.

120
00:06:16.967 --> 00:06:19.045
It's. you know.
first date jitters.

121
00:06:19.128 --> 00:06:20.665
-I understand.
-I'm so sorry.

122
00:06:20.747 --> 00:06:23.365
I'm just out of
practice. Would you

123
00:06:23.448 --> 00:06:24.986
