148
00:07:37.605 --> 00:07:38.809
Five weeks.

149
00:07:39.931 --> 00:07:44.003
Five weeks of 2:00
a.m. "you ups"

150
00:07:44.085 --> 00:07:45.790
and relearning how
to flirt. No. sir.

151
00:07:45.872 --> 00:07:47.535
You don't get to blow up my spot

152
00:07:47.617 --> 00:07:49.944
