160
00:08:12.003 --> 00:08:15.411
Eat
the rich! Eat the rich!

161
00:08:15.493 --> 00:08:16.698
Hey. hey! Ho. ho!

162
00:08:16.781 --> 00:08:18.900
Billionaires have got to go!

163
00:08:18.982 --> 00:08:21.018
Hey. hey! Ho. ho!

164
00:08:21.101 --> 00:08:23.179
Billionaires have got to go!

165
