hope he doesn't drown?

235
00:11:30.003 --> 00:11:31.832
Your move is to
sit tight while I get help.

236
00:11:31.915 --> 00:11:32.995
Hey. I'm gonna

237
00:11:33.078 --> 00:11:34.490
