238
00:11:39.185 --> 00:11:40.639
He's stuck in its teeth?

239
00:11:40.722 --> 00:11:42.467
They don't have teeth.

240
00:11:42.550 --> 00:11:43.921
It's baleen.

241
00:11:44.004 --> 00:11:44.918
What are you two.

242
00:11:45.001 --> 00:11:46.331
