258
00:12:30.699 --> 00:12:32.333
I'm looking
for the Coast Guard.

259
00:12:34.979 --> 00:12:36.931
Thar she blows.

260
00:12:39.798 --> 00:12:41.152
I don't see
any rescue boats.

261
00:12:42.457 --> 00:12:43.662
Yeah. me. neither.

