302
00:14:41.647 --> 00:14:43.184
Hey. I wanted to do that.

303
00:14:58.597 --> 00:15:00.218
Is
that Tripp Hauser?

304
00:15:00.301 --> 00:15:00.967
All right.
let's get in there.

305
00:15:01.050 --> 00:15:02.128
Bag. Cap.

306
00:15:10.229 --> 00:15:12.349
-God. TikTok is gonna love this.
-Buck?

307
00:15:12.432 --> 00:15:14.799
Okay. hey. come on.
people. Back it up.

308
00:15:14.882 --> 00:15:16.794
Back it up. Back
it up. Let's go.

309
00:15:22.361 --> 00:15:24.022
Come on.

310
00:15:27.553 --> 00:15:28.716
We got him!

311
00:15:30.628 --> 00:15:31.625
We got him.

312
00:15:43.050 --> 00:15:44.961
Thank you.

313
00:15:45.044 --> 00:15:47.412
You saved me from that fish.

314
00:15:47.494 --> 00:15:49.157
