357
00:18:32.426 --> 00:18:35.791
Stock prices for Hauser's
Techtonyx have sunk even deeper.

358
00:18:35.873 --> 00:18:37.453
If this trend continues.

359
00:18:37.536 --> 00:18:39.530
it'll be the
shareholders who are left

360
00:18:39.613 --> 00:18:41.898
