366
00:18:57.062 --> 00:18:58.930
Because I dropped out.

367
00:19:00.260 --> 00:19:02.172
I dropped out of high school.

368
00:19:03.209 --> 00:19:05.287
Order up for Athena.

369
00:19:22.569 --> 00:19:24.897
Ha-ha.

370
00:19:24.979 --> 00:19:27.171
Yeah. we'll see who's laughing
when you're walking home.

371
00:19:28.178 --> 00:19:30.214
-Give me that!
-Hey!

372
00:19:30.296 --> 00:19:32.499
-You two. knock it off!
-Tell him

373
00:19:32.581 --> 00:19:34.410
