374
00:19:34.493 --> 00:19:36.695
You're ten years old!

375
00:19:36.778 --> 00:19:39.146
And I've got more game than
you ever will. old man.

376
00:19:40.642 --> 00:19:41.763
Little demons.

377
00:19:44.297 --> 00:19:46.665
Wish they'd all just drop dead.

378
00:19:52.232 --> 00:19:53.852
Hey.

379
00:19:54.766 --> 00:19:57.010
Hey. what's going on back there?

380
00:20:00.790 --> 00:20:01.787
Kids?

381
00:20:04.571 --> 00:20:05.609
Kids?

382
00:20:06.939 --> 00:20:08.185
Wake up!

383
00:20:09.972 --> 00:20:11.758
