388
00:21:03.813 --> 00:21:05.600
Copy that. Ravi.
chock the tires.

389
00:21:05.683 --> 00:21:07.053
Buck. de-energize the bus.

390
00:21:07.136 --> 00:21:08.259
Hen. Eddie...

391
00:21:08.341 --> 00:21:09.588
Whoa.

392
00:21:09.671 --> 00:21:12.371
"Occifer."
I... I didn't mean to...

393
00:21:15.072 --> 00:21:16.568
Sir. have you been

