00:21:16.651 --> 00:21:18.396
-drinking?
-No. it's water.

395
00:21:18.478 --> 00:21:19.642
All right. guys.

396
00:21:19.724 --> 00:21:21.428
check him out. Thank
God this bus is empty.

397
00:21:21.510 --> 00:21:22.506
But it's not.

398
00:21:24.128 --> 00:21:25.749
All right.
Hen. Eddie. take the bus.

399
00:21:25.831 --> 00:21:27.784
Nathan. Taylor.
check out the driver.

400
00:21:31.149 --> 00:21:33.601
Chim. I don't think
