403
00:21:40.330 --> 00:21:42.034
All right. Garcia.
DeSoto. on the bus.

404
00:21:42.117 --> 00:21:43.156
Yes. Cap.

405
00:21:44.277 --> 00:21:45.192
Hey.

406
00:21:45.274 --> 00:21:47.393
