407
00:21:47.476 --> 00:21:48.806
those kids are on it. too.

408
00:21:48.888 --> 00:21:50.384
And they're smaller.
so it hit 'em harder.

409
00:21:50.467 --> 00:21:52.420
You thinking carbon monoxide?

410
00:21:52.503 --> 00:21:53.778
Wake up. kiddos.
It's time to go.

411
00:21:55.536 --> 00:21:56.450
It's not CO. Chim.

412
00:21:56.533 --> 00:21:58.776
I'm getting baseline
levels in here.

413
00:21:58.859 --> 00:22:00.521
All right.
guys. finish the evac.

414
00:22:00.604 --> 00:22:02.142
start positive pressure
ventilation till we can

415
00:22:02.225 --> 00:22:03.886
