glycol poisoning.

433
00:22:44.142 --> 00:22:46.677
Starts out as mild intoxication.

434
00:22:46.760 --> 00:22:49.253
But then the body
metabolizes to glycolic acid.

435
00:22:49.336 --> 00:22:50.416
