to wait for more RAs.

443
00:23:06.701 --> 00:23:08.155
Ethanol.

444
00:23:09.568 --> 00:23:12.061
Are you thinking what I
think you're thinking?

445
00:23:12.143 --> 00:23:13.889
Listen. I know it's
risky. but at least

446
00:23:13.971 --> 00:23:15.176
