into actual words

449
00:23:18.292 --> 00:23:19.331
so we know what
the plan is here.

450
00:23:19.414 --> 00:23:20.689
What's another word for ethanol?

451
00:23:25.272 --> 00:23:26.933
I'm so gonna get fired.

452
00:23:37.485 --> 00:23:40.228
Oh. no. this is not for
us. This is for the kids.

453
00:23:41.889 --> 00:23:43.676
This is Millie.

454
00:23:43.759 --> 00:23:45.213
ten-year-old female.

455
00:23:45.296 --> 00:23:47.415
Heart rate's 92. We've
administered saline

456
00:23:47.498 --> 00:23:49.948
