457
00:23:51.361 --> 00:23:53.937
This is Libby. 11. We
started her on 40 mils

458
00:23:54.020 --> 00:23:56.513
of Irish whiskey.
we're monitoring her.

459
00:23:56.596 --> 00:23:58.008
Clay and Dexter.

460
00:23:58.091 --> 00:23:59.795
-two tequila shots each.
-They're responding

461
00:23:59.878 --> 00:24:01.914
very well to treatment.

462
00:24:01.997 --> 00:24:03.658
-Bruh.
-Bruh.

463
00:24:05.319 --> 00:24:06.857
Nice work. you two.

464
00:24:10.347 --> 00:24:11.925
Hello?

465
00:24:13.421 --> 00:24:14.585
Yes. sir.

466
00:24:14.668 --> 00:24:16.786
Absolutely. right away.

467
00:24:18.365 --> 00:24:19.528
Everything okay?

468
00:24:19.611 --> 00:24:21.024
That was Chief Simpson.

469
00:24:21.107 --> 00:24:25.594
He has something
urgent to discuss.

470
00:24:25.677 --> 00:24:26.799
So he wants to see me?

471
00:24:26.881 --> 00:24:29.540
No. he wants to see me.

472
00:24:43.582 --> 00:24:44.621
They're right in here.

473
00:24:44.704 --> 00:24:46.116
Who's they?

474
00:24:51.351 --> 00:24:52.640
Chief Simpson.

475
00:24:52.722 --> 00:24:55.672
Wilson. I believe you
already know Mr. Hauser.

476
00:24:55.754 --> 00:24:57.375
You pumped krill
out of my lungs.

477
00:24:57.458 --> 00:24:58.663
Call me Tripp.

478
00:24:58.745 --> 00:25:00.699
Hen.

479
00:25:00.781 --> 00:25:02.859
And it was a team effort.

480
00:25:02.942 --> 00:25:05.393
Oh. this is Dawn. Myron

481
00:25:05.476 --> 00:25:07.346
