482
00:25:07.428 --> 00:25:09.340
-I know his name...
-It's Jensen.

483
00:25:09.422 --> 00:25:10.794
Okay. That doesn't sound right.

484
00:25:13.577 --> 00:25:15.572
Um. Tripp. you've...

485
00:25:15.655 --> 00:25:16.901
