510
00:26:12.861 --> 00:26:14.108
It's not just trucks. Wilson.

511
00:26:14.191 --> 00:26:16.766
95% of our budget
goes to staffing.

512
00:26:16.849 --> 00:26:18.387
A donation like this
would be a shot in the arm

513
00:26:18.470 --> 00:26:20.131
